## Audit Workflow

**Phase 1: Setup & Baseline** → Authenticate, navigate, capture baseline screenshots at all viewports
**Phase 2: Dimension Audit** → Execute dimension-specific checks per mode (quick/focused/full)
**Phase 3: Synthesis** → Prioritize findings, calculate baseline metrics, compare with prior audits
**Phase 4: Self-Review** → Verify evidence, check completeness, create beads issues

